        "content": "\n**Current state: zero automated tests.** No `tests/` directory, no test runner in `requirements.txt`. Everything below assumes adding `pytest`, `pytest-asyncio`, and `respx` (httpx-native mocking) as dev dependencies, plus a `tests/` package with a `conftest.py`.\n\n---\n\n",
